headline: Reflecting On Beverages, Alcohol, and Tobacco Stocks’ Q4 Earnings: Vita Coco (NASDAQ:COCO)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at beverages, alcohol, and tobacco stocks, starting with Vita Coco (NASDAQ:COCO).
